* Dinobot turned back towards Tavatron and saw her run off in the other 
direction, what was she doing?
The safer and more easier way was the long way, if they went up there then 
they would be further away from the base and would have to circle around the 
cliff edge just to get back on track.
Dinobot snarled as he began to follow Tavatron, he had to admit that it was 
easier but it would probably set them back a few cycles, and every cycle 
counted!
He stopped at the base of the trail and looked back towards the cliffs, who 
ever said that easier was better?
Dinobot turned back and watched Tavatron making her way up the steep trail, 
she was going much to slow!
He snarled as he sprinted up and came right behind Tavatron, he then lowered 
his head and began to push her from behind to give her the hint to climb 
faster.*

" Faster! Move!"

* Dinobot snarled, she had better pick up her pace or her hamstrings were 
his!*(sarcastic)
